Package: python3-truenas-pypam
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: C Python bindings for PAM
 This package provides Python bindings for the Pluggable Authentication
 Modules (PAM) library. It allows Python applications to authenticate users
 and manage PAM sessions using the system's PAM configuration.
 .
 The package includes both low-level PAM bindings and a high-level
 authenticator API that simplifies common authentication workflows with
 support for threaded conversation handling and session management.